#### File 7: `extensions/pulseboard/src/runtime-api.ts`

This is the critical difference vs IRC: there is no `openclaw/plugin-sdk/pulseboard`, so all imports come from existing generic SDK paths. The IRC `runtime-api.ts` imports from `openclaw/plugin-sdk/irc` which re-exports many IRC-specific and generic helpers. For PulseBoard, each thing must be traced to its generic SDK home.

