This defines all PulseBoard-specific TypeScript types. Key PulseBoard specifics:

- Auth: `apiUrl`, `apiKey`, `username` (maps to env vars `PULSEBOARD_API_URL`, `PULSEBOARD_API_KEY`, `PULSEBOARD_USERNAME`).
