| `createTopLevelChannelDmPolicySetter`, `createTopLevelChannelAllowFromSetter`, `applyAccountNameToChannelSection`, `patchScopedAccountConfig`, `DmPolicy`, `GroupPolicy`, `formatDocsLink`, `createSetupInputPresenceValidator`, `createAllowFromSection`, `createStandardChannelSetupStatus`, `setSetupChannelEnabled` | `openclaw/plugin-sdk/setup` |
| `ChannelSetupAdapter`, `ChannelSetupInput`, `ChannelSetupWizard`, `ChannelSetupDmPolicy` | `openclaw/plugin-sdk/channel-setup` |
