### Step 17 — `extensions/pulseboard/src/monitor.ts`

Gateway monitor — passive long-running loop. Since PulseBoard is fictional, it runs a wait loop listening for the abort signal rather than an actual WebSocket/polling connection:

```typescript
import { resolveLoggerBackedRuntime } from "./runtime-api.js";
import { resolvePulseBoardAccount } from "./accounts.js";
import { handlePulseBoardInbound } from "./inbound.js";
import { sendMessagePulseBoard } from "./send.js";
import { getPulseBoardRuntime } from "./runtime.js";
